CF-GeS-1015, CF-GeS-1082, CF-GeS-1092(?)</p>

<p class="MsoNormal"><i>Cissonius</i> (incl. ev. Varianten):</p>

<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-ansi-language:IT" lang="IT">- Germania
Inferior: - - Germania
Superior: CF-GeS-1011, CF-GeS-1012</span></p></div>
